SUMMARY:Day 2: Move-in Day
DESCRIPTION:\nHighlights:\n• Drive to campus\n• Check-in\n• Unload car\n• Move-in and set up room\n• Shop early morning on move-in day to beat crowds and ensure full stock of popular items\n• Bring a detailed packing list and dorm room dimensions to avoid over-purchasing\n• Check if your college has a move-in essentials list or partnerships with specific retailers for discounts\n• Consider purchasing bulky items (pillows\, mattress pad) before arriving to save luggage space
